{"tid":2080723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你問心，今日係咪驚到連《榮光》都唔敢唱⋯","createTime":"2020-06-26T15:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T07:45:35.000Z","uid":7542,"like":170,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"bf3d01cab9348b88246c5df82b40f2976503caeb","tid":2080723,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:31:29.000Z","msg":"你唔夠膽上街，我明白<br />\n你唔夠膽表達政見，我理解<br />\n但係你思想上嘅退縮，我冇辦法接受<br />\n<br />\n每一代、每一個地方嘅抗爭<br />\n都有一班人頂住白色恐怖去創作歌曲<br />\n就係為咗凝聚民意團結民心<br />\n納粹對抗運動、韓國光州事件、烏克蘭革命等⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n如果你今日覺得失落、冇力、恐懼、迷惘<br />\n唔知道呢場運動應該點樣繼續行落去<br />\n<br />\n我懇求你睇一睇呢條片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=65dd4a3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a><br />\n<br />\n入面介紹咗五場對抗極權嘅抗爭<br />\n你會睇到前人有幾勇敢、無私<br />\n我更加希望你可以留意下入面嘅六首歌<br />\n串連埋一齊就係一個抗爭嘅詩篇曲目<br />\n尤其留意佢嘅歌詞<br />\n<br />\n剪片嘅時候其實真係剪到係咁喊<br />\n由舊年六月到而家嘅回憶<br />\n每個無辜犧牲嘅義士面孔<br />\n<br />\n如果你今日同我講<br />\n你唔再夠膽上街唱《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n我請你唔好唔記得佢嘅曲調歌詞<br />\n<br />\n因為呢首係屬於香港人嘅歌<br />\n屬於一個時代抗爭嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da7363d5fba7b5fd9578caaaea0f0f8bc44488f","tid":2080723,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e66ca4b208627414658d513d130419f4774350","tid":2080723,"uid":244818,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:36:36.000Z","msg":"71見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借個位 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a><br />\n立會事實處 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2072298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2072298</a><br />\n眾志 蘋果 DW德國之聲訪問手足 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2063033\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2063033</a><br />\n抗爭文獻館 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2071555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2071555</a><br />\n暴政粵譯 第六課 小心那些準軍事組織 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2058004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2058004</a>"},{"pid":"9a8eabf4596a9eda0ae601f1aa73579b6d8042c4","tid":2080723,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:37:02.000Z","msg":"sor 借個位黎推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【文宣核彈】聯合國成堆專家要求中國撤回國安法，並呼籲國際共同監察中國<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2080705\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2080705</a>"},{"pid":"99baed0155ffdec7f5ac9c4acbe4e768d4e79b5e","tid":2080723,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:37:46.000Z","msg":"鬥紅鬥藍算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b37bcdca6c26b2e6891323c5f6eb9329b6172c","tid":2080723,"uid":154486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FFNl5HyhhWwg&d=jQldmXM9xAXOA%2BwUl6G2h3Qc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=8c8d743d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/FNl5HyhhWwg</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">吾等烏克蘭，榮光猶在，自由尚存人間；<br />\n吾等同胞，青天之上，命運再展笑顏。<br />\n吾等強敵，去如朝露，終須消散；<br />\n是以兄弟，吾等國土，將必歸屬吾身。<br />\n<br />\n鮮血遍地，魂魄飛逝，全為吾等自由；<br />\n以此足證，吾等兄弟，皆為哥薩克民族！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e91c946417f2cef4cd1416d2dd39e789581f4676","tid":2080723,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa06b346a4e2dc2f925a85b121ed250ca94a21f","tid":2080723,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7da7363d5fba7b5fd9578caaaea0f0f8bc44488f","ti